==English==

===Adjective===
'''intramuscular'''

# Inside a muscle or the muscles

====Etymology====
From Late Latin '''[[intramuscularis]]''', from prefix '''[[intra-]]''', ''within'', + '''[[musculum]]''', ''muscle'', diminutive of '''[[muscus]]''', ''mouse'', + adjective suffix '''[[-alis]]'''

